<div style=3D"font-size:10px;margin-top:1px">Anzeige</div><p>The kite is ax=
ially symmetric to the symmetry diagonal between the two non-equal angles. =
When the half kite has a right angle opposite to the dividing symmetry axis=
, only then it has an circumcircle. Its center is in the middle of the symm=
etry axis.</p>
